        {
            "title": "OpenAI反駁《華爾街日報》有關營收疑慮的報導",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - OpenAI週二對《華爾街日報》的一篇報導作出反擊,該報導稱該公司未能達成新用戶和營收的內部目標,引發管理層對未來資料中心支出資金的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司在社交媒體平台X上回應稱,「Codex的突破性增長、在每個雲端平台上的企業服務、唯一重要的消費者應用程式、為加速而建立的運算策略,以及全球最優秀的研究人員」都展現了強勁的業績指標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》報導稱,首席財務官Sarah Friar向公司領導層表達了擔憂,若營收增長未能加速,公司可能無法支付未來的運算合約費用。報導還指出,近幾個月來,董事會成員更仔細地審查了公司的資料中心交易,並質疑執行長Sam Altman在業務放緩期間爭取額外運算能力的努力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-834df991-dfcf-37a1-b0d0-653ff3d90514-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OpenAI週二向彭博社發表聲明稱,其業務「全力運轉」,企業和廣告業務正在增長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/openai%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E-173855088.html",
