        {
            "title": "十年長約鎖定印度！輝達豪擲1.3億美元在班加羅爾租12層辦公大樓 全球AI研發重心轉移？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mQUBPpTeX2g9QxblOSp0bA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f61cb7ac8276b1f526af952fa1ef190f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E7%B4%84%E9%8E%96%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6-%E8%BC%9D%E9%81%94%E8%B1%AA%E6%93%B21-3%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%9C%A8%E7%8F%AD%E5%8A%A0%E7%BE%85%E7%88%BE%E7%A7%9F12%E5%B1%A4%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83ai%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC%E9%87%8D%E5%BF%83%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB-160009820.html",
